title: The 4-Hour Zeiter Cut 3/19: Putin, Biden, March Madness, Marvel, Anthony Edwards
itunes:title: The 4-Hour Zeiter Cut 3/19: Putin, Biden, March Madness, Marvel, Anthony Edwards
description:
On this very special 4-Hour Zeiter Cut Jack and Miles discuss Biden calling Putin a 'killer', Putin challenges Biden to debate, Biden keeps falling up the stairs of Air Force One, March Madness has officially begun, there's a new Falcon and the Winter Soldier trailer, and rookie Anthony Edwards puts up 42 last night.
